      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/aquamarine/{size}/11614_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-07-15T08:07:17.192Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Po une s’thashe eshte e bukur o Vloraa. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/blush.png?v=5\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\"> Por ka nje bukuri shprehese. S’eshte e thene me qene perfekt per te qene i bukur, shume fytyra s’te thone asgje edhe pse mund te mos te te shqetesojne dhembet si misra. Edhe shija ka arsyet e saj te nderlidhura (nuk eshte amstel se keshtu me pelqen).<br>\nJu mos u merrni me Marionin po na sugjeroni ca filma t’bukur. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slightly_smiling_face.png?v=5\" title=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slightly_smiling_face:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 31,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 42671,
      "post_number": 33,
      "username": "BeluliXVI",
      "name": "Beluli-XVI",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/belulixvi/{size}/241_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-07-15T09:11:19.003Z",
      "cooked": "<p>filmi  ‘‘ndergjegja’’, ka muzike te papare ! ritem i trazuar shoqeruar, ne background , nga tingulli i mprehte i organos kishtare.<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=5\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> kombinim fantastik ! ne fakt  eshte muzike teper moderne per kohen, muzika qe luhej edhe ne kinematografine italjane apo evropiane ate periudhe…  si duket godtija ne art nuk kishte filluar akoma qe e kane toleruar si kolone zanore ne kete film.</p>\n<p>-kshu si film pastaj, eshte futja kot… i thote ajo e fejueshmja heroit kryesor : ''une te dua shume ty Kujtim… por po te vetdenoncohesh e te futesh ne burg, do te dua akoma me shume…<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>\n<div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"nQ1LNHSOU6U\" data-youtube-title=\"\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 42672,
      "post_number": 34,
      "username": "Pjetermustakuqi",
      "name": "A.P",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/pjetermustakuqi/{size}/11417_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-07-15T09:20:25.617Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Lexova para dy ditesh ne nje blog italian, se Marloni i Tikut i’a kishte hip Xheims Dinit. Mardhanje e eger fare,sado-mazo,i fikte cinaren n’trup. Marloni kurre s’e deshi Xheimsin,theshte,e linte te shifte kur ky pallonte meshkuj te tjere,si dhe e linte si klysh mas dere dhe s’kishte te drejte te hynte,pa i dhan leje. Ishte nje tip qe kishte shkrujt ni liber per ket pune;“tomorrow never comes!”. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=5\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
